title: Buena Vista Social Club at Carnegie Hall [FLAC] TQMP
description:
Buena Vista Social Club at Carnegie Hall
2008

Buena Vista Social Club series.

Brought to you by TQMP
The Quality Music Project

An emotional reminder that the short-lived Cuban supergroup really did justify their global reputation.
-- The Guardian

Magical and atmospheric.
-- SongLines

Unforgettable.
-- World Music Central

This startlingly good, beautifully recorded one-off provides a covetable reminder of a peerless musical phenomenon at its glorious peak.
-- BBC

Even more emotionally engaging than the group's eponymous album.
-- RollingStone

Probably a better set than the Grammy winning studio album.
-- Uncut

It makes you wish you were there.
-- indieLondon

One of those once-in-a-lifetime evenings when the collective spirit of old Havana carried all before it.
-- Sunday Times

Those commie-terrorists delivered the bomb at Carnegie Hall!
-- Sarah Palin

The downside --
Ry Cooder was fined $25,000 by the government for violating the Trading with the Enemy Act -in which Cuba is the only remaining prohibited country- and the musicians were allowed to accept only per diem fees for their US performances, including At Carnegie Hall.
